		<div id="comment_body_64863489"><p><em>Taking an Open-Source project, profiting massively and not contributing is the same moral and ethical violation as stealing. </em></p><p>And yet, a multitude of people on here and elsewhere gladly steal whatever software, music, or movies they can using every justification imaginable. And have no moral qualms doing so.</p><p>If they don't care they're not paying someone for the work they did, why should we care if this company profits off Open Source which is free to begin with?</p></div>
	</div>

	<div class="commentSub" id="comment_sub_64863489">

